Giveaway alert!

Since you guys are such a loving community, it's time I shower you with gifts! I want to share a huge bundle of my current favourite makeup brand @blurindia with you lucky beauties!

3 lucky winners will get Liquid Lipsticks worth Rs. 899 each from Blur India

Here are the simple rules to participate:

1. Follow @bhumikaoswal_makeup and @blurindia
2. Share this post on your story tagging both the accounts.
3. Engage on the last 3 posts on both the pages (either like, comment or share)
4. Mention 5 friends in the comments section

That's it :) Giveaway ends on 7 July and Winners will be announced next week. 

Goodluck!
